      <!-- Practical exercise -->
      <section>
        <h2>Practical exercise - Quest validation</h2>

        <div class="quest-objective">
          <p>Run the verification script to confirm that Git is installed and configured correctly on your machine.</p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Bash</strong> (Linux / macOS / Git Bash on Windows):</p>

        <pre data-lang="bash"><code>bash verifier.sh</code></pre>

        <p><strong>PowerShell</strong> (Windows):</p>

        <pre data-lang="powershell"><code>.\verifier.ps1</code></pre>

        <p>The script checks three things:</p>

        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Git is <span class="highlight">installed</span> on your machine</li>
          <li>Your <span class="keyword">name</span> is configured (<span class="git-cmd">user.name</span>)</li>
          <li>Your <span class="keyword">email</span> is configured (<span class="git-cmd">user.email</span>)</li>
        </ol>

        <p>If all three steps pass, congratulations! You are officially a member of the Archivists' Guild. The next quest awaits.</p>
      </section>

